1
00:00:10,254 --> 00:00:12,381
<font color="#ffff00">SEMUA KARAKTER, TEMPAT,
ORGANISASI, DAN KEJADIAN</font>

2
00:00:12,382 --> 00:00:13,335
<font color="#ffff00">DALAM DRAMA INI ADALAH FIKTIF</font>

3
00:00:21,115 --> 00:00:22,416
Saeroyi.

4
00:00:39,217 --> 00:00:40,518
Aku...

5
00:00:42,553 --> 00:00:44,397
sudah berlutut di hadapanmu.

6
00:01:00,029 --> 00:01:01,622
Kenapa kau begini?

7
00:01:02,490 --> 00:01:05,459
Ke mana prinsip hidup
yang kau pertahankan itu?

8
00:01:10,039 --> 00:01:12,299
Ini cukup untuk membuatmu berlutut?

9
00:01:16,754 --> 00:01:19,598
Pada akhirnya, kau menyerah
karena aku lebih berkuasa.

10
00:01:26,139 --> 00:01:27,940
Di mana Jang Geun-won?

11
00:01:35,940 --> 00:01:38,826
Padahal aku berharap
kau bisa menjadi hiburan terakhirku.

12
00:01:42,905 --> 00:01:44,874
Ternyata kau membosankan.

13
00:01:47,368 --> 00:01:50,087
Kau tak ada bedanya dengan pengemis.

14
00:01:54,125 --> 00:01:56,761
Tapi karena kau berlutut,

15
00:01:59,464 --> 00:02:02,433
aku harus membuang putraku kembali.

16
00:02:39,337 --> 00:02:42,014
Musuhku ini akhirnya berlutut juga.

17
00:02:43,257 --> 00:02:44,433
Sekarang...

18
00:02:45,843 --> 00:02:47,436
bagaimana perasaanmu?

19
00:02:53,809 --> 00:02:55,277
Aku merasa menyedihkan.

20
00:02:56,854 --> 00:02:58,155
Benarkah?

21
00:03:01,192 --> 00:03:04,286
- Pergi.
- Bagaimana perasaanmu, Pak?

22
00:03:10,326 --> 00:03:12,211
Dengan melihatku berlutut,

23
00:03:12,954 --> 00:03:14,421
apa kau senang?

24
00:03:24,340 --> 00:03:26,016
Apa kau puas?

25
00:03:27,927 --> 00:03:29,979
- Sekarang...
- Sampai sekarang,

26
00:03:30,763 --> 00:03:33,899
aku hidup membawa dendamku padamu.

27
00:03:38,896 --> 00:03:41,073
Presdir Jangga, Jang Dae-hee.

28
00:03:41,899 --> 00:03:43,284
Musuhku.

29
00:03:44,610 --> 00:03:47,830
Pria yang merusak hidupku,
tapi dia juga...

30
00:03:49,240 --> 00:03:50,833
pria yang hebat.

31
00:03:54,787 --> 00:03:57,798
Walau nilai kita berbeda,
aku mengakui kehebatanmu.

32
00:03:59,458 --> 00:04:00,801
Aku...

33
00:04:03,462 --> 00:04:05,639
mengikuti jejakmu

34
00:04:06,424 --> 00:04:08,142
seumur hidupku.

35
00:04:12,597 --> 00:04:13,898
Kupikir

36
00:04:15,891 --> 00:04:18,444
pertarungan ini memang pantas.

37
00:04:19,770 --> 00:04:21,989
- Tunggu.
- Tapi pria itu...

38
00:04:23,649 --> 00:04:24,992
mengancamku...

39
00:04:25,943 --> 00:04:28,621
untuk berlutut
dengan menculik orang terdekatku.

40
00:04:32,658 --> 00:04:35,827
Aku membuang beberapa belas tahun
untuk mengikuti jejak

41
00:04:35,828 --> 00:04:37,463
pria tua menjijikkan ini?

42
00:04:40,833 --> 00:04:42,885
Aku menyesal

43
00:04:46,714 --> 00:04:48,015
menyia-nyiakan hidupku.

44
00:04:51,594 --> 00:04:52,978
Lihat hasilnya.

45
00:04:53,971 --> 00:04:55,731
Kau berlutut di depanku, 'kan?

46
00:04:56,474 --> 00:04:58,233
Kadang untuk keuntungan...

47
00:05:01,479 --> 00:05:02,905
Ayo pergi, Seung-kwon.

48
00:05:03,272 --> 00:05:04,615
Baik.

49
00:05:27,797 --> 00:05:30,015
Setelah beberapa belas tahun,

50
00:05:31,092 --> 00:05:32,434
aku baru mengenalmu.

51
00:05:50,828 --> 00:05:53,738
<font color="#ffff00">EPISODE TERAKHIR</font>

52
00:05:53,739 --> 00:05:55,082
Benar.

53
00:05:55,658 --> 00:05:57,668
Park Saeroyi atau siapalah itu.

54
00:05:58,244 --> 00:06:00,963
Ayo kita bunuh Jo Yi-seo dahulu.

55
00:06:21,434 --> 00:06:24,361
Tak usah buang tenaga. Kalian diam saja.

56
00:06:27,690 --> 00:06:29,074
Angkat itu.

57
00:06:39,410 --> 00:06:41,161
Astaga, aku takut sekali.

58
00:06:41,162 --> 00:06:42,421
Kenapa?

59
00:06:42,830 --> 00:06:45,466
Kau pikir kami takut dengan itu?

60
00:06:47,001 --> 00:06:48,510
Kalian konyol.

61
00:06:48,878 --> 00:06:51,972
Serang mereka pada hitungan ketiga.

62
00:06:54,341 --> 00:06:55,258
Ayo ke sini.

63
00:06:55,259 --> 00:06:56,685
Satu.

64
00:06:56,886 --> 00:06:58,803
Dua. Tiga.

65
00:06:58,804 --> 00:07:02,316
Jang Geun-soo, semangat! Bertahanlah!

66
00:07:10,691 --> 00:07:12,326
Tangkap gadis itu.

67
00:07:13,152 --> 00:07:14,569
Sialan.

68
00:07:14,570 --> 00:07:16,205
Jangan berani mendekat!

69
00:07:21,202 --> 00:07:22,795
Apa yang kau lakukan?

70
00:07:24,163 --> 00:07:25,422
Dia menyuruhku...

71
00:07:27,041 --> 00:07:28,300
untuk bertahan.

72
00:07:43,849 --> 00:07:46,360
Kau tahu, 'kan? Ini hal berbahaya.

73
00:07:49,814 --> 00:07:51,073
Aku...

74
00:07:52,399 --> 00:07:53,951
akan menyelamatkan Yi-seo.

75
00:07:55,486 --> 00:07:57,496
Aku tahu, karena itu kita ke sana.

76
00:07:59,515 --> 00:08:01,442
Kau harus pilih prioritasmu.

77
00:08:02,685 --> 00:08:03,601
Apa?

78
00:08:03,602 --> 00:08:05,729
Semua akan berantakan

79
00:08:05,730 --> 00:08:08,282
bila kau ragu ambil keputusan.

80
00:08:08,899 --> 00:08:10,367
Sekalipun

81
00:08:11,152 --> 00:08:13,912
aku dan kau bisa terluka,

82
00:08:14,905 --> 00:08:17,875
juga mati, Yi-seo tetap harus selamat.

83
00:08:20,161 --> 00:08:21,879
Begitu rupanya.

84
00:08:22,830 --> 00:08:26,341
Namun, aku tak bisa memaksamu
untuk tetap ikut denganku.

85
00:08:28,127 --> 00:08:31,138
Dasar aneh.
Kalau begitu, kenapa kau ajak aku?

86
00:08:34,383 --> 00:08:35,642
Yi-seo.

87
00:08:36,302 --> 00:08:38,353
Walau terkadang kurang ajar,

88
00:08:39,054 --> 00:08:41,065
kini dia keluarga.

89
00:08:42,099 --> 00:08:43,734
Dia juga penting bagiku.

90
00:08:43,934 --> 00:08:46,070
Tujuan kita harus sama...

91
00:08:47,104 --> 00:08:48,655
agar bisa bekerja sama dengan baik.

92
00:08:51,901 --> 00:08:53,243
Terima kasih.

93
00:08:53,652 --> 00:08:54,828
Tak masalah.

94
00:08:56,030 --> 00:08:58,916
Walau kau mati,
aku akan tetap selamatkan Yi-seo.

95
00:09:21,514 --> 00:09:22,648
Kau tak apa-apa?

96
00:09:23,891 --> 00:09:25,818
Ini kali pertamamu ditusuk, 'kan?

97
00:09:26,811 --> 00:09:31,198
Sia-sia berlagak keren
seperti yang kau lihat di film.

98
00:09:31,440 --> 00:09:32,991
Inilah realitanya.

99
00:09:42,284 --> 00:09:44,378
Kau ternyata pria sejati.

100
00:09:45,037 --> 00:09:46,338
Diam di tempat.

101
00:09:53,587 --> 00:09:54,972
Cukup.

102
00:09:57,216 --> 00:09:58,725
Kau tak tangkap Jo Yi-seo?

103
00:09:59,385 --> 00:10:00,519
Kau bisa kehilangan dia.

104
00:10:04,682 --> 00:10:05,858
Benar juga.

105
00:10:08,143 --> 00:10:09,528
Ayo berangkat.

106
00:10:22,449 --> 00:10:25,586
Kau sudah dapat semua yang kau inginkan,
termasuk Jangga, 'kan?

107
00:10:25,995 --> 00:10:28,088
Jangan ikut campur.

108
00:10:32,418 --> 00:10:34,052
Yang kuinginkan?

109
00:10:38,799 --> 00:10:41,184
Aku tak pernah dapatkan
hal itu seumur hidupku.

110
00:10:42,928 --> 00:10:44,354
Tak pernah sama sekali.

111
00:10:51,061 --> 00:10:52,404
Namun,

112
00:10:54,565 --> 00:10:57,159
kau dan aku ternyata memang saudara.

113
00:11:00,779 --> 00:11:02,247
Apa maksudmu?

114
00:11:03,907 --> 00:11:05,292
Kita selalu gunakan...

115
00:11:07,244 --> 00:11:08,837
cara yang salah.

116
00:11:13,876 --> 00:11:16,261
Dia sedang apa? Kau tak mau ikut?

117
00:11:19,506 --> 00:11:20,933
Pegang dia.

118
00:11:56,543 --> 00:11:57,970
Hei, Anak Kecil!

119
00:11:58,379 --> 00:12:00,046
Menyerah sajalah!

120
00:12:00,047 --> 00:12:02,057
Kau tak akan bisa lari dari kami!

121
00:12:02,675 --> 00:12:05,352
Kau saja yang menyerah, dasar preman!

122
00:12:09,056 --> 00:12:11,108
- Tangkap dia.
- Baik.

123
00:12:18,315 --> 00:12:19,741
Astaga.

124
00:12:20,526 --> 00:12:22,160
Dia benar-benar keras kepala.

125
00:12:53,600 --> 00:12:54,818
Sial.

126
00:13:12,995 --> 00:13:14,379
Tabrak dia.

127
00:13:49,948 --> 00:13:52,200
Kantong udaranya berfungsi sempurna.

128
00:13:52,201 --> 00:13:53,919
Untunglah.

129
00:13:56,622 --> 00:13:57,964
Sialan.

130
00:13:58,248 --> 00:14:00,050
Apa ini?

131
00:14:00,876 --> 00:14:02,094
Sial.

132
00:14:06,048 --> 00:14:07,349
Bos?

133
00:14:09,927 --> 00:14:11,269
Yi-seo.

134
00:14:15,057 --> 00:14:16,400
Bos...

135
00:14:17,392 --> 00:14:18,693
Bos!

136
00:14:34,660 --> 00:14:35,794
Kau tak apa-apa?

137
00:14:38,038 --> 00:14:39,548
Aku dengar kau terluka.

138
00:14:40,999 --> 00:14:44,928
Untuk apa kau ke sini? Apa kau gila?

139
00:14:46,296 --> 00:14:47,973
Park Saeroyi!

140
00:14:55,305 --> 00:14:56,857
Kau membantuku.

141
00:14:57,933 --> 00:15:00,861
Kau datang sendiri untuk mati, 'kan?

142
00:15:02,771 --> 00:15:04,072
Saeroyi.

143
00:15:06,358 --> 00:15:07,701
Hee-hoon.

144
00:15:08,777 --> 00:15:10,704
Untuk apa kau datang ke sini?

145
00:15:12,531 --> 00:15:15,125
Aku datang setelah lapor polisi.

146
00:15:17,911 --> 00:15:19,880
Apa kau tak bisa pergi saja?

147
00:15:20,247 --> 00:15:22,248
Dasar pengecut.

148
00:15:22,249 --> 00:15:23,717
Aduh, sakit.

149
00:15:26,378 --> 00:15:27,721
Sialan.

150
00:15:28,714 --> 00:15:31,224
Seung-kwon, kau baik-baik saja?

151
00:15:32,593 --> 00:15:35,687
Astaga, Direktur Jo. Senang mendengarmu
memanggilku begitu.

152
00:15:36,597 --> 00:15:37,680
Seung-kwon.

153
00:15:37,681 --> 00:15:40,358
Ya, aku tahu prioritasku.

154
00:15:43,896 --> 00:15:47,240
Cepat pergi. Aku akan urus ini.

155
00:15:51,695 --> 00:15:52,871
Ayo pergi.

156
00:15:57,075 --> 00:15:58,418
Sial.

157
00:16:02,289 --> 00:16:03,632
Choi Seung-kwon.

158
00:16:14,343 --> 00:16:15,560
Hajar dia.

159
00:16:22,726 --> 00:16:26,696
Astaga, dahulu kau teman kami.

160
00:16:26,897 --> 00:16:28,281
Kau tak kenal ampun.

161
00:16:29,191 --> 00:16:30,909
"Jangan ragu."

162
00:16:31,318 --> 00:16:33,537
Bukankah itu yang sering kau katakan?

163
00:16:35,155 --> 00:16:36,706
Sudah kuduga,

164
00:16:37,449 --> 00:16:39,876
- kau lebih cocok dengan kami.
- Tidak.

165
00:16:42,579 --> 00:16:44,673
Aku juga mahir melayani tamu.

166
00:17:16,905 --> 00:17:18,415
- Kau baik-baik saja?
- Ya.

167
00:17:19,032 --> 00:17:20,834
Untuk apa kau ke sini?

168
00:17:21,076 --> 00:17:22,419
Ayo.

169
00:17:26,873 --> 00:17:28,633
Aku teringat saat itu.

170
00:17:29,251 --> 00:17:31,011
Ketika kita berlari di Itaewon.

171
00:17:32,170 --> 00:17:34,431
Untuk apa kau tiba-tiba membicarakan itu?

172
00:17:36,008 --> 00:17:38,143
Karena aku sangat merindukanmu.

173
00:17:49,980 --> 00:17:51,364
Kau selalu...

174
00:17:52,983 --> 00:17:54,909
berusaha keras untukku selama ini.

175
00:17:56,570 --> 00:17:58,288
Kau selalu terluka.

176
00:18:01,950 --> 00:18:03,376
Apa ini?

177
00:18:05,162 --> 00:18:07,130
Kau sungguh baik-baik saja?

178
00:18:11,877 --> 00:18:13,094
Kenapa bisa begini?

179
00:18:21,345 --> 00:18:22,896
Pikiran...

180
00:18:25,891 --> 00:18:27,317
dan hatiku

181
00:18:35,025 --> 00:18:36,451
dipenuhi olehmu.

182
00:18:44,618 --> 00:18:46,503
Mungkin ini juga yang kau rasakan.

183
00:18:46,953 --> 00:18:48,213
Ternyata...

184
00:18:48,830 --> 00:18:50,298
ini membuatku gugup.

185
00:18:52,918 --> 00:18:53,834
Bos.

186
00:18:53,835 --> 00:18:55,178
Aku mencintaimu.

187
00:19:01,385 --> 00:19:02,852
Aku mencintaimu, Yi-seo.

188
00:19:09,768 --> 00:19:11,361
Aku sangat mencintaimu.

189
00:19:34,000 --> 00:19:35,927
Dasar gila.

190
00:20:00,986 --> 00:20:02,361
Pergi! Lari!

191
00:20:02,362 --> 00:20:04,572
Bagaimana aku bisa meninggalkanmu?

192
00:20:04,573 --> 00:20:06,583
Apa kau sengaja mau mati sendiri?

193
00:20:08,869 --> 00:20:10,619
Polisi akan meneleponmu.

194
00:20:10,620 --> 00:20:13,256
Angkat dan beri tahu posisi kita.

195
00:20:18,545 --> 00:20:21,347
Kalian berdua bersenang-senang, 'kan?

196
00:20:23,216 --> 00:20:25,226
Percaya padaku dan pergilah.

197
00:20:27,179 --> 00:20:28,688
Yi-seo.

198
00:20:31,308 --> 00:20:33,276
Dasar konyol.

199
00:20:33,935 --> 00:20:35,445
Bila kau mati,

200
00:20:36,229 --> 00:20:37,614
aku juga akan mati.

201
00:20:38,315 --> 00:20:40,200
Cepat pergi. Cepat!

202
00:20:41,610 --> 00:20:43,286
Hei!

203
00:20:53,288 --> 00:20:54,672
Sialan.

204
00:20:59,461 --> 00:21:01,587
Kau mau mati, 'kan?

205
00:21:01,588 --> 00:21:04,933
Aku dan Seung-kwon datang
untuk mempertaruhkan nyawa.

206
00:21:05,842 --> 00:21:09,562
Nyawamu sama sekali tak berharga bagiku.

207
00:21:11,097 --> 00:21:12,357
Dasar gila.

208
00:21:18,897 --> 00:21:20,022
Bos!

209
00:21:20,023 --> 00:21:21,407
Dasar berengsek!

210
00:21:25,779 --> 00:21:27,247
Lihat apa kau?

211
00:21:44,130 --> 00:21:45,473
<i>Hari ini,</i>

212
00:21:48,385 --> 00:21:49,727
<i>semua akan berakhir.</i>

213
00:22:00,480 --> 00:22:01,864
Berengsek!

214
00:22:06,319 --> 00:22:08,079
Mati saja kau!

215
00:22:08,280 --> 00:22:11,541
Seperti ayahmu!

216
00:22:17,330 --> 00:22:20,258
Bagaimana bisa kau masih mengaku manusia?

217
00:22:34,439 --> 00:22:38,618
Yi-seo, Geun-soo, Ho-jin,

218
00:22:39,069 --> 00:22:40,578
juga ayahku.

219
00:22:43,365 --> 00:22:45,750
Apa kau tak merasa bersalah sama sekali?

220
00:22:48,495 --> 00:22:50,672
Ketika makan daging babi,

221
00:22:50,955 --> 00:22:52,715
apa kau merasa bersalah?

222
00:22:53,333 --> 00:22:54,333
Apa?

223
00:22:54,334 --> 00:22:56,844
Karena babi-babi itu,

224
00:22:58,171 --> 00:22:59,555
semuanya lenyap.

225
00:23:00,173 --> 00:23:01,516
"Bersalah"?

226
00:23:02,008 --> 00:23:03,258
Omong kosong apa itu.

227
00:23:03,259 --> 00:23:06,479
- Dasar bajingan!
- Tutup mulutmu, Berengsek!

228
00:23:16,689 --> 00:23:18,324
Mati kau, Berengsek!

229
00:23:18,983 --> 00:23:20,067
Mati saja kau!

230
00:23:20,068 --> 00:23:21,244
Tunggu.

231
00:23:24,739 --> 00:23:26,457
Hari ini datang juga.

232
00:23:26,783 --> 00:23:28,501
Kau keren.

233
00:23:33,415 --> 00:23:34,882
Seperti kata Saeroyi,

234
00:23:35,250 --> 00:23:36,968
aku akan pergi dengan tenang.

235
00:23:43,550 --> 00:23:45,435
Bagaimana dengan mereka?

236
00:23:47,303 --> 00:23:48,604
Apa?

237
00:23:49,013 --> 00:23:50,806
Lihatlah keadaanku.

238
00:23:50,807 --> 00:23:53,609
Aku sendiri bahkan tak bisa bertahan.

239
00:23:54,519 --> 00:23:56,603
Biarkan mereka di sini dahulu...

240
00:23:56,604 --> 00:23:57,780
Hentikan.

241
00:24:00,859 --> 00:24:02,744
Tak usah bicara lagi.

242
00:24:07,407 --> 00:24:10,126
Kau mulai membuatku menyesal

243
00:24:11,494 --> 00:24:13,504
pernah bekerja untukmu.

244
00:24:17,250 --> 00:24:18,718
Bos sejati

245
00:24:19,669 --> 00:24:21,888
adalah orang
yang berani bertanggung jawab.

246
00:24:28,052 --> 00:24:29,270
Mati!

247
00:24:29,637 --> 00:24:31,105
Mati saja!

248
00:25:04,172 --> 00:25:06,932
Tunggu. Di sana. Berhenti di depan.

249
00:25:45,004 --> 00:25:48,015
Mati saja kau, dasar zombi.

250
00:25:53,429 --> 00:25:55,773
Aku tidak seperti dahulu.

251
00:25:59,519 --> 00:26:01,153
<i>Kau harus ingat ini.</i>

252
00:26:02,647 --> 00:26:04,281
<i>Bila kau mati,</i>

253
00:26:04,982 --> 00:26:06,450
<i>aku juga akan mati.</i>

